This is my first time posting two “ Unedited Photos” I never thought I would do so. 
I have changed to my lighting a few weeks ago. I now use 2 or 3 lights vs. 1…these are so clean I figured I would “float them out there “ and see what happens .
In frame : the beautiful @iumnjmiss .I think the incredible pics are a combination of lighting and incredible makeup by @mobilebeautyservicesllc . My tip of the day is : Hiring a good Makeup artist makes a world of difference. They know what makeup look colors etc.  photographs best . Going forward I will recommend @mobilebeautyservicesllc for all shoots . Take great photos to incredible photos for a few dollars .
